{"tid":1949324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓衛生部一架載有醫療物資包機於馬尼拉墜毀爆炸！","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T04:56:20.000Z","uid":63113,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"81050371edd1a580f7ed689f4dbf86e22bcdc2a2","tid":1949324,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5c04761bdfaf1774d674eb55895c0403f7c68c","tid":1949324,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"天誅"},{"pid":"28e5df6ae27cbb3b6ad18abb8547b7521565984e","tid":1949324,"uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"菲律賓首都馬尼拉驚傳墜機意外，當地民眾目擊，尼諾伊艾奎諾機場（Ninoy Aquino International Airport）一架班機於晚間8時30分起飛時，墜毀在跑道上，瞬間爆炸燒成一團火球，附近民眾看得驚呼連連。據悉，該班機疑似為政府租用的獅航班機，載運加拿大病患正在飛往日本東京羽田的途中，起飛時不幸墜毀，全員罹難。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓紅十字會證實，班機上搭載8名乘客，包含3名隨行醫護、3名機組人員以及1名病患。菲媒報導，墜機航班為RP-C5880小型飛機，機上疑似載有醫療物資用品，機上8人有6人是菲律賓籍，1名加拿大籍、1名美國籍，8人皆不幸罹難。<br />\n<br />\n附近民眾聽到巨響嚇得紛紛跑出來查看，根據目擊者拍下的影片顯示，現場因墜機爆炸，火勢猛烈，熊熊火光燃燒照亮天際，黑煙瀰漫機場跑道，消防員撲滅火勢後，只剩飛機框架殘骸遺留在場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1679478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1679478&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=0042549e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1679478</a>"},{"pid":"1f9508faf568965649bbf93008fbf749afa1a7d1","tid":1949324,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da8f435ed2b879bbd636fb58896331f220bdcb8a","tid":1949324,"uid":65091,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img